<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.3.6">
<l>aṉṉaiyeṉ ceyyile ṉūreṉ collileṉ ṟōḻimī</l>
<l>reṉṉai yiṉiyumak kācai yillai yakappaṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉai yamarar mutalvaṉ vaṇṭuva rāpati</l>
<l>maṉṉaṉ maṇivaṇ ṇaṉvācu tēvaṉ valaiyuḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Whatever mother does, what? Whatever the village says, what, friend?</l>
<l>You have now no affection for me. I have fallen into</l>
<l>the net of Vācutēvaṉ, the one of sapphire colour, the king,</l>
<l>the liberal lord of Dhvāraka, first among the immortals of old.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
